1) Create Empty Project

2) Create UI package and fragments package inside that

3) Create blank fragments and remove unnecessary parts

4) Convert Fragment Layout to Constraint Layout in XML files of activities

5) Create  Android resource directory navigation inside res and create navigation resource file

6) Add fragments to navigation resource file, make necessary design changes for fragments if there is need

7) Do View Binding in build.gradle, then in each fragment

8) Create vector asset for FAB

9) Add FAB and change the color of vector asset in the coding part using app:tint



